    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Install-Oh-my-zsh-In-Linux"><a href="#Install-Oh-my-zsh-In-Linux" class="headerlink" title="Install Oh-my-zsh In Linux"></a>Install Oh-my-zsh In Linux</h3><blockquote><p><strong>Install</strong></p></blockquote><pre><code class="shell">apt install -y gitapt install -y zshsh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh)&quot;sh -c &quot;$(wget https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)&quot;</code></pre><hr><blockquote><p><strong>My Theme</strong></p></blockquote><ul><li>1</li></ul><pre><code class="shell">cd .oh-my-zsh/custom/themes/vim robbyrussell-ascii.zsh-theme</code></pre><ul><li>2</li></ul><pre><code class="shell">local ret_status=&quot;%(?:%{$fg[green]%}&gt;:%{$fg[red]%}&gt;%s)&quot;PROMPT=&#39;${ret_status} %{$fg[cyan]%}%~ %{$reset_color%} $(git_prompt_info) # &#39;ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_PREFIX=&quot;%{$fg[blue]%}git:(%{$fg[red]%}&quot;ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_SUFFIX=&quot;%{$reset_color%} &quot;ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_DIRTY=&quot;%{$fg[blue]%}) %{$fg[yellow]%}x%{$reset_color%}&quot;ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_CLEAN=&quot;%{$fg[blue]%})&quot;</code></pre><ul><li>3</li></ul><pre><code class="shell">vim .zshrcZSH_THEME=&quot;robbyrussell-ascii&quot;</code></pre><hr><blockquote><p><strong>效果如图</strong></p></blockquote><p><img src="/2019/04/08/oh-my-zsh/oh-my-zsh.png" alt="oh-my-zsh.png"></p>]]></content>
    
